Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.68,0:00:27.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}救救我
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.09,0:00:29.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,哎呀，姊姊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.31,0:00:36.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您醒了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,感覺如何?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.11,0:00:42.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&335580\4c&335580}做美夢了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&2D5680\4c&2D5680}請您再快一點
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你再著急也於事無補
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您倒是冷靜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,但您的未婚妻
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不知道已經吃了多少苦頭了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你確定沒搞錯嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.89,0:02:41.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.94,0:02:42.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世一定在齋森家
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}美世一定在齋森家
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}看您遲遲不醒
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.32,0:02:52.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我還以為您的心臟停止跳動了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為…為什麼要這樣對我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真是令人厭惡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼不好好做傭人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,或者乾脆死在什麼地方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,真是不知死活
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳必須立刻和久堂大人解除婚約
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.89,0:03:18.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,妳要親口對他說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,「我要和您解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.68,0:03:27.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,對姊姊來說，做久堂大人的妻子過於辛苦了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.82,0:03:36.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,身穿如此華美的和服
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.37,Dial-CHI,？,0,0,0,,您覺得自己有這個資格嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.37,0:03:42.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.54,0:03:45.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您會答應回絕這樁婚事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不然，您這件漂亮的和服
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就會被我親手
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,裁剪得和您一樣不堪入目
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.39,0:04:05.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,這麼昂貴的和服，您都能讓他賣給您
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:11.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,解除婚約想必不是問題吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.65,0:04:14.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我和久堂大人定親後
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,就會把幸次先生還給您
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好了，姊姊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,您會對久堂大人說什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,住…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,住?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}住手
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1450,1004)\bord0\shad0}不對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我想聽的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}不是這句話
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,請姊姊務必親口說
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,「我要解除婚約」
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,在這裡放棄一定很簡單
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,可唯獨這件事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,唯獨這件事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不願向任何人讓步
