Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,不出聲嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,姊姊未免太沒用了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.65,0:05:31.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,…不要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我不會提出那種請求
